The paper deals with using convolutional neural networks for image recognition tasks, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of deep learning and machine learning techniques, which are relevant to machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses image retrieval, which falls under information retrieval (cs.IR) and multimedia (cs.MM).
